<URL>https://github.com/jcofer555/vm-backup-and-restore/releases/download/2025.12.17.01/unraid-vm-backup-and-restore-2025.12.17.01-noarch-1.txz</URL>
<SHA256>0fe19a574a6ce2eef9be1b464a965665bcfcca4188f9f35a9d6169b282bf7985</SHA256>
